Re: A short description about myself
by chikara » Thu 04.01.2010 10:43 pm Nakagawa Izumi wrote:Hmm, interesting. In which instances should I use the "ya" particle instead of the "to" particle?You use "ya" when the list is not exhaustive and "to" when the list is. "ya" can imply "etc".
